{"word":"συμφράζομαι","slug":"συμφράζομαι","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>συμφράζομαι</b></el> <el>(<a href='S:active signification'><a href='S:Active voice'>act.</a></a> <el>συμ-φράζω</el>) (<a href='S:future tense'>fut.</a> <el>-άσομαι</el>) (epic <el>-άσσομαι</el>) (<a href='S:perfect tense'>perf.</a> <el>-πέφρασμαι</el>) </el><p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><a href='S:Medium, Middle'>Mid.</a>:— <i>to join in considering, to take counsel with</i>, <a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:dative'>dat.</a>, <b><a href='S:Odyssey'>Od.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><el>τίς τοι συμφράσσατο βουλάς</el>; who <i>imparted</i> his counsels to thee? <b><a href='S:Odyssey'>Od.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>3. </b><i>to contrive</i>, <b><a href='S:Hesiod'>Hes.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Sophocles'>Soph.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><a href='S:active signification'><a href='S:Active voice'>Act.</a></a> <i>to mention at the same time</i>, <b><a href='S:Strabo'>Strab.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}